trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en sorterad lista över <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TimerEventSubscriptionCollection represents the queue of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> objects associated with a workflow instance and provides methods to manage this queue.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En TimerEventSubscriptionCollection representerar kön för <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>objekt som hör till ett arbetsflöde instansen och ger metoder för att hantera den här kön.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>

trans-unit.source: Subscriptions are ordered in the queue based on their <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values; those with smaller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values are positioned before those with larger <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values.
trans-unit.target: Prenumerationer är sorterade i kö baserat på deras <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>värden; dem med mindre <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>värden är placerad före de med större <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>värden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the methods provided by this class to manage the collection of active timer event subscriptions exposed by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> for each workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda de metoder som tillhandahålls av den här klassen för att hantera mängden active timer händelseprenumerationer som exponeras av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>för varje arbetsflödesinstans.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can use <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A> to add or remove subscriptions from the timer queue.
trans-unit.target: Du kan använda <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A>eller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A>att lägga till eller ta bort prenumerationer från timerkön.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Whenever the first element in the timer queue changes, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService> is called to cancel the timer event that was previously at the beginning of the queue and schedule the new timer event.
trans-unit.target: När det första elementet i timerkön ändras den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService>anropas för att avbryta timerhändelse som tidigare var i början av kön och schemalägga nya timerhändelse.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService>

trans-unit.source: Subscriptions in the queue are positioned based on their <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName> values; those with smaller values are positioned in front of those with larger values.
trans-unit.target: Prenumerationer i kön placeras baserat på deras <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName>värden; de med lägre värden placeras framför dem med högre värden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the new subscription is added at the beginning of the queue, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called to cancel the timer event that was previously at the beginning of the queue and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName> is called to schedule the new timer event.
trans-unit.target: Om den nya prenumerationen har lagts till i början av kön <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>anropas för att avbryta timerhändelse som tidigare var i början av kön och <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName>anropas för att schemalägga nya timerhändelse.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An enumerator remains valid as long as the collection remains unchanged.

trans-unit.source: If changes are made to the collection, such as adding, modifying, or deleting elements, the enumerator is irrecoverably invalidated and its behavior is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Om ändringar görs i samlingen, till exempel att lägga till, ändra eller ta bort element, uppräknaren blir inaktuella och sitt beteende är odefinierad.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator does not have exclusive access to the collection; therefore, enumerating through a collection is intrinsically not a thread safe procedure.
trans-unit.target: Uppräknaren har inte exklusiv åtkomst till samlingen; uppräkning av en samling är därför är inte en säker tråd-procedur.
